 Joaquim Chissano International Conference Centre  www.ametrade.org  With over 400 participants originating from Mozambique’s Mining, Energy, Oil and Gas industries, MMEC presents a unique event that connects the main stakeholders of these sectors. The conference features a dedicated networking platform that allows you to maximize your participation!  MMEC gathers the most influential stakeholders – financiers, investors, national and international operators, government officials, etc – in Mozambique’s Mining, Oil & Gas and Energy sectors.  Attending MMEC 2021 will grant you access to the major-league who is active in these sectors. You will also benefit from the knowledge presented in the focused conference stream. This is what makes MMEC an important asset in establishing your investment strategy in the country for the next two years.  #MMEC 